Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:53.66,default,,0,0,0,,The ship of hope, Espoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望の船 エスポワール
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:56.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは借金を抱え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:59.47,default,,0,0,0,,A gambling ship where those\Ndesperate in debt gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:01:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き詰まった者たちを集めた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:01:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブル船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:02.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで開催された勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:02.14,default,,0,0,0,,And that's where\NIto Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:06.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限定ジャンケンに挑んだ伊藤開司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:05.53,default,,0,0,0,,...joins the game of Restricted\NRock Paper Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.09,default,,0,0,0,,But early in the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:10.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 開始早々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:10.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その寿命ともいうべき星を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:12.11,default,,0,0,0,,he lost his stars which is\Nequivalent to his life gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:12.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立て続けに失ってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:16.12,default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.\NThanks for the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:16.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほな 俺はこれで ごちそうさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.83,default,,0,0,0,,In this hopeless situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼はこの劣悪な状況の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:24.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人の男 古畑 安藤と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:24.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運命共同体を組み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:24.67,default,,0,0,0,,he teamed up with 2 guys,\NFuruhata and Ando,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残りへの道を踏み出す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.92,default,,0,0,0,,to try to create\Na way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人合わせた手持ちのカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ４枚 パー１枚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:33.33,default,,0,0,0,,The cards they have are\N4 Scissors and 1 Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:43.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か俺 希望が わいてきました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.75,default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I'm starting\Nto feel more hopeful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.88,default,,0,0,0,,It's better to have three of us\Nthan one. We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:47.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人よりは３人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:47.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間ですよね 俺たち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救えねえやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:52.46,default,,0,0,0,,Hopeless fool! We're still three\Npieces of useless trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょせん俺たち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズ３人じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:56.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,状況は大して変わってねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:56.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この甘ったれが！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.89,default,,0,0,0,,The situation isn't\Nany better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:56.68,default,,0,0,0,,You stupid naive idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:02:00.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お？お前 カード１枚 どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.09,default,,0,0,0,,What happened to\None of your cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:04.47,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ando asked me\Nfor it, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… 安藤さんが１枚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持たせてくれって言うから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:07.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？渡したのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.46,default,,0,0,0,,- What?! You gave it to him?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎　分からねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.30,default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:13.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつは星２つでカード０
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.64,default,,0,0,0,,He has 2 stars and\Nno cards at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった１枚のカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,欲しい状態だったんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:16.64,default,,0,0,0,,A card is exactly\Nwhat he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのカードが手に入ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負に行くに決まってるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:20.29,default,,0,0,0,,Once he has one, he'll\Ndefinitely go try his luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつを捜すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.51,default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.60,default,,0,0,0,,Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.38,default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこだ 野郎　どこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.39,default,,0,0,0,,Where... Where's that fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　あそこです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.63,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:51.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ちやがれ　安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:51.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ お前？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.21,default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:49.87,default,,0,0,0,,Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.14,default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の邪魔をするな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.34,default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.91,default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere with the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下がれ 下がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.44,default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.52,default,,0,0,0,,Get back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:57.42,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.12,default,,0,0,0,,Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:02:59.96,default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.42,default,,0,0,0,,Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:03.66,default,,0,0,0,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.20,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった　チョキなら あいこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.63,default,,0,0,0,,Alright! It's a draw\Nif it's Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星２つなら安藤も抜けやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.13,default,,0,0,0,,With 2 stars, Ando won't be\Nable to leave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.28,default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:36.07,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,Game
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すいません　勘弁してください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.92,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.38,default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get 5 stars\Nfor everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とかみんなの星を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５つにしようと思って…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うそつけ！勝ったら俺たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏切るつもりだったんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:47.15,default,,0,0,0,,Liar! You were going to\Nbetray us if you win, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな！誤解です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.37,default,,0,0,0,,It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.27,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Let's get rid of this guy!\NThis traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　こいつもう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切りましょうよ　こんな裏切り者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.77,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, please trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:56.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　信じてください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:59.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 裏切る気なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:59.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,毛ほどもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:59.22,default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention\Nof betraying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見苦しい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.63,default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear the sight\Nof you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんまり人をナメるな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.69,default,,0,0,0,,Don't take people for fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:10.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が止めに入った時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:10.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はチェック宣言前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:09.79,default,,0,0,0,,I had to stop you before\Nyou declared check.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ勝負はやめられたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.02,default,,0,0,0,,You could have stopped\Nif you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:15.89,default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing\Nas trust there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じろも くそもねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝っていたら 俺たちを切っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:19.28,default,,0,0,0,,If you won,\Nthen we will be cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:24.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけは疑いようがねえのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.27,default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:30.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが安心しろ　切らねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:30.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:27.27,default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.66,default,,0,0,0,,I won't get rid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.19,default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪しきを切ってたら 団結はねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.10,default,,0,0,0,,We won't be united if\Nwe remove the bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.28,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし安藤を切れば理由はどうあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その事実が足かせとなり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.51,default,,0,0,0,,If I cut Ando off,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.21,default,,0,0,0,,regardless of the reason,\Nwe won't benefit from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:44.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いよいよとなれば こいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:44.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を切るやつだと考える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:43.09,default,,0,0,0,,You'll begin to think that I'll cut\Nyou off when something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人で１単位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運命共同体と誓ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:48.42,default,,0,0,0,,Not long after we vowed\Nto share a common destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その舌の根も乾かぬうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グループの心はバラバラ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:52.03,default,,0,0,0,,the group starts to fall apart\Njust like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.63,default,,0,0,0,,So we can't cut him off...\Neven if we want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから切らねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切りたくても切らねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.32,default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 ここからは頑張って協力して…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.37,default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best to assist you\Nfrom now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力じゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.87,default,,0,0,0,,It's not assisting !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:09.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１頭のライオンが３つに分かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:09.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きていけるかって言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:09.70,default,,0,0,0,,If a lion is split into three,\Ncan it survive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.84,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそったれが！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ　くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.84,default,,0,0,0,,Darn! Darn! Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かろうじてグループは維持された
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.59,default,,0,0,0,,The group managed to\Nkeep together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 状況は星を１つ減らし窮地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.09,default,,0,0,0,,but their situation seems\Ngrimmer now with one less star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:33.63,default,,0,0,0,,All they have left\Nare these 4 Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:33.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手元に残されたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:33.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この４枚のチョキのカードのみ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった１枚のパーを使っちまって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.53,default,,0,0,0,,By using up the only Paper\Ncard we have,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このバランスの悪いカードで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.80,default,,0,0,0,,it's all your fault that we\Nhave to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗り切らなきゃいけないんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.38,default,,0,0,0,,...with these unbalanced cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:49.52,default,,0,0,0,,B-But it's not all my fault that the\Nrest of the cards are unbalanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,の 残りのカードの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランスが悪いのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺だけの責任じゃないっす
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.69,default,,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- It's your cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もともと古畑さんが持ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:55.28,default,,0,0,0,,...that are unbalanced\Nright from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードのバランスにも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題があったわけで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:59.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前！言うにこと欠いて！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:59.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１度 言ってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:59.05,default,,0,0,0,,You! How dare you!\NTry saying that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.49,default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.72,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.61,default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランス？バランスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.50,default,,0,0,0,,Balance? It's the balance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.24,default,,0,0,0,,The cards keep crossing\None another in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:11.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幾度となくカードが交差する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:11.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その無限の交差の中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:13.85,default,,0,0,0,,In that infinite crossing,\Na thought began to form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,編み込まれていく ある思考
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それによって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解きほぐされていく結び目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.40,default,,0,0,0,,And with that,\Na knot is untied...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる　いや 勝てるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:23.66,default,,0,0,0,,We could win! We might\Nactually be able to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.39,default,,0,0,0,,The door which\Nwas closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:30.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開きそうにもなかった扉が今
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:30.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きしみつつ動き出した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.78,default,,0,0,0,,...now seemed to\Nopen up a crack,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから差し込む光明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:34.16,default,,0,0,0,,letting a beam of light\Nshine through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:38.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨てたもんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:38.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちにもまだツキがある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:38.66,default,,0,0,0,,All is not lost yet!\NLuck is still with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.16,default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グズグズしちゃいられねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:42.90,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:47.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分担して動こう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:47.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は金で星を仕入れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.51,default,,0,0,0,,Let's split up.\NI'll go buy the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その間にお前たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:52.51,default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, you guys go search\Nfor a man with my description!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから俺が言う条件の男を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,探してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.26,default,,0,0,0,,Description?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.51,default,,0,0,0,,The description Kaiji\Ngave was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの言う条件とは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず手持ちのカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９枚の男を見つけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:00.49,default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, a man with 9 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.31,default,,0,0,0,,Then check his deck\Nwith 2 duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後の２回の勝負を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェックする
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,順番はどうあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーとチョキを使っていること
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:07.25,default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the sequence, make sure\Nhe used Rock and Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い換えれば９枚のカードのうち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.34,default,,0,0,0,,That means, a man who\Nused Rock and Scissors,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーとチョキの２枚を使い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:15.05,default,,0,0,0,,and who is left with 7 cards\Nout of his 9 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り７枚となった男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むろんカイジの思いついた策は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して必勝の策ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.80,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the plan\NKaiji thought of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.95,default,,0,0,0,,...was not a foolproof plan\Nto winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:22.69,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji knows that best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはカイジ自身が分かっている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 星１つでは挑めない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.47,default,,0,0,0,,And furthermore,\None star is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:30.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の前に星を２つに戻すことが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:30.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必須条件なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.88,default,,0,0,0,,He'll need to go back to having\N2 stars before he duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.48,default,,0,0,0,,But this proved to be\Nthe most difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし これが至難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあっ？ダメダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.78,default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を売れ？何 言ってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.57,default,,0,0,0,,Sell my stars?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.17,default,,0,0,0,,Don't kid me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１千万なら考えてやってもいいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:42.29,default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it for 10 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰１人 まともな交渉には応じない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.93,default,,0,0,0,,No one took him seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が それも無理ないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.66,default,,0,0,0,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:53.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ皆 勝負の渦中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:53.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時期が悪かったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.56,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is still in\Nthe middle of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.62,default,,0,0,0,,The timing is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１～２時間 過ぎれば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星の余裕が確定する者が現れ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.12,default,,0,0,0,,After one or two hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.41,default,,0,0,0,,those with extra stars\Nwill appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:02.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交渉も成り立ったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.86,default,,0,0,0,,and they will be open\Nto negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だ… やめてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か助けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:09.43,default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.42,default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だ 嫌だ　助けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.14,default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か助けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:21.76,default,,0,0,0,,These guys are crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:22.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつら… 狂ってやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:23.93,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.77,default,,0,0,0,,There's a man who is\Nleft with 7 cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ７枚になったばかりの男が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 安藤が見張ってます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星のほうは？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.47,default,,0,0,0,,Ando's watching him now. How are\Nyou doing with the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.91,default,,0,0,0,,I haven't bought\Nthem yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが… まだ買えてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな… どうするんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:38.25,default,,0,0,0,,No way! What should we do?\NAt this rate...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グズグズしてると…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.75,default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:43.96,default,,0,0,0,,Not many people who fulfil\Nthe conditions are left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:44.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,条件をそろえた男が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:44.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう何人も残ってるはずねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:47.02,default,,0,0,0,,He might be the last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら最後の１人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:50.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,千載一遇のチャンス　だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.26,default,,0,0,0,,This is our best bet!\NBut...! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:09:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝利への道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:09:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その１歩目が途切れている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:59.83,default,,0,0,0,,The path to victory is blocked\Nat the very first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:05.00,default,,0,0,0,,To walk this path,\Nyou must not dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この道を行くには
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身を翻さなくてはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:10.51,default,,0,0,0,,No matter how frightening it is,\Nyou must not back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:11.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなに恐ろしくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:11.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは臆してはならない道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは飛べる距離なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:13.38,default,,0,0,0,,This is the distance\NI have to leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:14.90,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:18.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:18.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　こっちです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.91,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臆さない　ただ行くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.25,default,,0,0,0,,No fear... Just move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どいつだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.50,default,,0,0,0,,Ando! Which one is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:40.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:40.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ソファーに座ってる男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:38.70,default,,0,0,0,,That guy! That guy on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:44.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど こりゃ好都合だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.48,default,,0,0,0,,I see, this is convenient\Nfor us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.77,default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:49.15,default,,0,0,0,,Did he avoid playing with\Nthose with many stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつは星の多い相手の勝負を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,避けてなかったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.20,default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？ええ… 確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:55.15,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he did seem to be avoiding\Ngames with those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星の多いやつとは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに勝負を避けてました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして分かったんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.39,default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:02.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつが星１つの男と
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:02.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負してたのを見たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:01.12,default,,0,0,0,,I saw him playing with\Na guy with one star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通 星１つの相手とは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦いたくないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:05.44,default,,0,0,0,,You usually won't want to play\Nwith someone with one star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か自分の手で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破滅に突き落とすみたいで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel bad if\Nyou were the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気が引けるだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.77,default,,0,0,0,,...who pushed the guy\Noff the cliff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも やつが星１つの男に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った時の顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:15.78,default,,0,0,0,,But he looked like he was\Ngloating when he won.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,してやったりって感じだった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星が多い相手を嫌がるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.31,default,,0,0,0,,And why does he avoid\Nthose with many stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らくやつの戦略は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:23.78,default,,0,0,0,,I fear his strategy is like that\Nof a contrarian in roulette.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルーレットなんかでよくある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆張り
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.20,default,,0,0,0,,He only plays against...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限定ジャンケンなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星１つか２つの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.17,default,,0,0,0,,...those with 1 or 2 stars in\NUnrestricted Rock Paper Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち目のやつのみを相手にする
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:34.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうやって勝ちを拾う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:34.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱ってる相手専門のハンター
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:33.39,default,,0,0,0,,He's a hunter who seeks out\Nweaker opponents to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.09,default,,0,0,0,,He's just like a hyena!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハイエナ野郎ってことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星１つの俺がやつの傍らで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頭でも抱えてりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.52,default,,0,0,0,,If I, with my one star,\Nlook distressed in front of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうから声をかけてくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.44,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんなやつ相手にして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫なんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:46.16,default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure you'll be fine\Nagainst someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.87,default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's the ideal opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:50.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや やつこそ理想の相手だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.29,default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを確認してる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつの余裕の表情を見ても分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:54.06,default,,0,0,0,,Judging from his relaxed\Nexpression when he checks his cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:59.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつは間違いなくバランス派だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:59.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランス派？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.48,default,,0,0,0,,he definitely belongs to\Nthe balanced type!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.06,default,,0,0,0,,Balanced type?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.28,default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことなんすかね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:03.68,default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶんカードのことだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.65,default,,0,0,0,,I guess he meant the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:09.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に何を出すか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:09.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,唯一 ｺﾝﾄﾛｰﾙできるところだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:09.54,default,,0,0,0,,The only type who can control\Nwhat card to play next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ古畑さんはどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.46,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:15.42,default,,0,0,0,,Why are you left with\N3 Scissors and 1 Paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ３枚 パー１枚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残したんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？考えてもしょうがないから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.26,default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was useless\Nto dwell on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き当たりばったりで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,適当に出してただけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.00,default,,0,0,0,,so I just played my cards\Nat random.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:25.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？普通もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:25.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランスを考えますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:24.94,default,,0,0,0,,What?! But won't you usually\Nthink about balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランス？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ その要するに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.24,default,,0,0,0,,Balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.62,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, to put it simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 僕たちが困っている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:33.25,default,,0,0,0,,one should avoid being left with 4\NScissors cards like what we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ４枚っていう状態を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,避けるっていうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:37.11,default,,0,0,0,,Usually you'd want to leave\Nyourself with an alternative...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:37.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通 カードをギリギリまで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:37.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選択することができるように
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり偏った残し方は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しないっていうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:40.04,default,,0,0,0,,...instead of an unbalanced\Nhand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし自分のカードが偏っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.85,default,,0,0,0,,If your cards are of only\None kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことが相手に知られたら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目も当てられないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:46.19,default,,0,0,0,,and your opponents find out,\Nthen there's no way to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ だからたぶん…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.47,default,,0,0,0,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.39,default,,0,0,0,,Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだよ　カイジさんは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:49.96,default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.34,default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.49,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji figured out\Nthat guy has 2 Rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつの手持ちカード７枚のうち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グー チョキ パー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.71,default,,0,0,0,,2 Scissors and 2 Paper\Namong his 7 cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれ２枚ずつは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あると読んだんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:02.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:02.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は残る１枚が何かだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:59.31,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:02.56,default,,0,0,0,,But what's the last card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:08.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ！そうだよ　分かりきったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.32,default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.05,default,,0,0,0,,- The answer is Paper !\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.63,default,,0,0,0,,In a hand of 9 cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちの９枚のカードのうち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２回の勝負で グーとチョキの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを使用すると
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:16.12,default,,0,0,0,,after using a Rock and\NScissors in 2 duels,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この７枚となる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランス重視の者であれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.69,default,,0,0,0,,you'll end up with\N7 cards like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.97,default,,0,0,0,,Those who place emphasis\Non balance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次にグーやチョキのカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使用する場合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.00,default,,0,0,0,,...will avoid using a Rock\Nor Scissors next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードが偏ることとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.12,default,,0,0,0,,Thus they'll use a Paper\Ncard instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:30.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆえにパーのカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:30.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使用するという公算が成立する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:29.74,default,,0,0,0,,...to avoid upsetting the balance\Nof their deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:34.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,危機的状況の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:34.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは探り当てた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.80,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji had sensed it\Nin this crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝利へのタイトロープ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.08,default,,0,0,0,,A tightrope towards victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし しょせんは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮定で塗り固めた理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.58,default,,0,0,0,,But it's just theory based on\Nassumptions after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の気まぐれで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たやすく破綻する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.95,default,,0,0,0,,The opponent's fickleness can\Neasily topple that theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.45,default,,0,0,0,,Now Kaiji's leaving his destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 この吹けば飛ぶような理に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちは自らの運命を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,預けようとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:50.96,default,,0,0,0,,in the hands\Nof this fragile reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:58.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック　セット
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.46,default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.70,default,,0,0,0,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.56,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:01.57,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む 神様　１度だけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.07,default,,0,0,0,,Please, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.50,default,,0,0,0,,Just once...\NJust this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ１度だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡らせてください
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.06,default,,0,0,0,,Let us cross this\Nflimsy bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:14.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この か弱い橋を！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:32.33,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.86,default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:36.38,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.07,default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？てことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.00,default,,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:43.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.21,default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.44,default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったあ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った　勝ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.94,default,,0,0,0,,He won! He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星１つで大騒ぎしやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.55,default,,0,0,0,,Making such a fuss over\None star...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:54.85,default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戻れ　席に着け
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.84,default,,0,0,0,,Come back! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:00.99,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう ひと勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.53,default,,0,0,0,,One more round!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… ちょっと待ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.42,default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:08.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,深呼吸 深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.77,default,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath.\NDon't get too worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだよ 熱くなっちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ったから勢いに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗りたいってのは分かるけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.28,default,,0,0,0,,I know you want to capitalise\Non your winning streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:15.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ 分かってるじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.12,default,,0,0,0,,So you do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らこそ深呼吸してみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:18.76,default,,0,0,0,,If you get it, you guys \Nshould take deep breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:22.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちはまだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:22.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を取っていかなきゃならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.74,default,,0,0,0,,We still have many more\Nstars to obtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:25.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ったら前へ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:25.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前のことだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:25.35,default,,0,0,0,,Push forward if you win.\NThat should be the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:27.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で… でもカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.95,default,,0,0,0,,B-But Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のやつは次に何 出すかもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.59,default,,0,0,0,,You won't know what\Nhe'll put out next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:34.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから任せとけ　必ず勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:34.09,default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!\NI'll win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ははーん　こいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緊急避難のように体制を組んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:40.73,default,,0,0,0,,These losers are clinging to each\Nother like refugees in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズの集まり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:45.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ツキに見放された
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:45.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人組ってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.70,default,,0,0,0,,They're just a 3-man group\Nabandoned by Lady Luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.30,default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　受けてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.17,default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.78,default,,0,0,0,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:50.91,default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流れが読めねえ 調子乗りが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:55.43,default,,0,0,0,,Arrogant idiots who can't\Nread the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らに２連勝があるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.65,default,,0,0,0,,There will be no 2 straight\Nwins for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,踏みつぶしてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.17,default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:04.52,default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.29,default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冷静に勝負を考えてる人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.26,default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was a cool-headed\Nguy bent on winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:10.76,default,,0,0,0,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.69,default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じっくり理詰めで勝負してたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.71,default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's impossible\Nto get 9 stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても時間内に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９個の星なんて無理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.27,default,,0,0,0,,...if we go around\Nplaying like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんはそれを実感したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.97,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji understands that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勢いに乗って奇跡の連勝に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走り出さない限り…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:24.60,default,,0,0,0,,Without a miraculous\Nwinning streak,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちに生き残りはない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.61,default,,0,0,0,,we won't be able to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.61,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　もう１度 パー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.47,default,,0,0,0,,Please! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.35,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが… 当然の結果じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.96,default,,0,0,0,,Fool! That's obvious\Nfrom the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:47.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度続けて同じカードで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:47.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てるとでも思ってんのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:46.96,default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could win with\Nthe same cards twice in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？待てよ　てことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:50.56,default,,0,0,0,,Wait! This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.76,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.57,default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:54.57,default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:55.57,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうひと勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.46,default,,0,0,0,,One more game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.33,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきはお前の望みを
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてやったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.17,default,,0,0,0,,I did what you asked\Njust now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度はそっちが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の望みを聞く番だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:04.78,default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn\Nto listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.89,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手にすることないです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.97,default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから お前らはダメなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.55,default,,0,0,0,,If so, then you guys\Nare doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人じゃ何も決められないクズが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.05,default,,0,0,0,,Garbage that can't even decide\Nanything on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:22.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,挑発 挑発
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:22.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,超見え見えの挑発っす
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.80,default,,0,0,0,,He's just taunting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.03,default,,0,0,0,,He's obviously provoking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来いよ カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.53,default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱気になって座り込んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は増えねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:28.40,default,,0,0,0,,The stars won't increase even\Nif you sit there in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 行きましょう カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.97,default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 下がれない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.93,default,,0,0,0,,No... I won't back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.02,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつの言うとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下がっても星は増えない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.28,default,,0,0,0,,He's right! The stars won't\Nincrease if we back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:40.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 言ってんの　星１つなんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.88,default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NYou have only one star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よしてよ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勘弁してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.68,default,,0,0,0,,- Give it up, Kaiji!\N- Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ　なぜ俺の演技が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からない？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.86,default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Why can't you see\Nthat I'm acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:51.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,演技？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:51.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２戦目の負けは計算 まき餌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:48.81,default,,0,0,0,,Acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.58,default,,0,0,0,,The loss in the 2nd duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:54.01,default,,0,0,0,,...was a calculated bait!\NNow the fish is biting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 魚がエサに食いついたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ　２連勝だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.39,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Nit'll be 2 straight wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２連勝なんて どこにそんな勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.77,default,,0,0,0,,Two straight wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.06,default,,0,0,0,,Why is he so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちにチョキしかない以上…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.35,default,,0,0,0,,With only Scissors cards\Non our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:11.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が２回続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:11.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーを出すってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:11.28,default,,0,0,0,,the opponent has to\Nput out 2 Paper in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの あり得ないっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:13.65,default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:16.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんには確信があるんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.91,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji is confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにバランス派のハイエナが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.35,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, a balance type\Nlike that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この後 ２連続パーを出すとは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えにくい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.52,default,,0,0,0,,...isn't likely to put out\N2 Paper cards back to back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に出すとしたら それは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.74,default,,0,0,0,,Even if he would,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.76,default,,0,0,0,,it's only when he's sure\NKaiji would put Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:28.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジがグーを出すと確信した時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:32.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいはパーを出しておけば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:32.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心と考えた時である
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:32.42,default,,0,0,0,,Or when he feels that\Nit's safe to use Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはつまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:33.76,default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:40.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:40.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤　カイジさん 勝つよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.01,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.38,default,,0,0,0,,Ando! Kaiji will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:44.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつは２度 続けてパーを出す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:41.30,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.94,default,,0,0,0,,He'll put 2 Paper consecutively.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことっすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.94,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:48.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつのバランス理論だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.46,default,,0,0,0,,It's his balance theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の３戦目でよみがえったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:52.68,default,,0,0,0,,His rule for balancing his deck\Ncomes into play in the next duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつのバランス理論が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:56.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからカイジさんを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:56.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,執拗に勝負に誘った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.22,default,,0,0,0,,That's why he tried so hard\Nto get Kaiji to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランス理論がよみがえった？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.55,default,,0,0,0,,The balance theory comes\Ninto play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度続けてチョキを出した
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.86,default,,0,0,0,,Will he even imagine\Nthat Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残りのカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚ともチョキだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:06.56,default,,0,0,0,,...is left with 2 Scissors after\Nusing 2 Scissors in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつがそんな想像すると思うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつは１戦目の時に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:12.60,default,,0,0,0,,He probably thought that the cards\NKaiji had in the first duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんのカードの内訳は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ２枚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてグーとパーが１枚ずつと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えたはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:16.30,default,,0,0,0,,will be 2 Scissors, 1 Rock\Nand 1 Paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 カイジさんの残りカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.72,default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Nhe'd predict that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーとパーが１枚ずつ もしくは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どちらか２枚と考えている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:24.31,default,,0,0,0,,...Kaiji has 1 Rock and 1 Paper,\Nor 2 cards of one type left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり３戦目以降は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーさえ出せば勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.92,default,,0,0,0,,Which means that as long as\Nhe uses Paper, we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:33.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪くてもあいこ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:33.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けはないと確信したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:33.12,default,,0,0,0,,And at the very worst, we draw.\NHe believes he won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:34.15,default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:39.30,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji waited until that guy believed\Nin that scenario to fight it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは やつがその思考に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,至るのを待って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負にいったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.42,default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:44.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　カイジは待った
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.66,default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Kaiji had waited for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:48.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵が自らぬかるみに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:48.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足を踏み入れるのを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.77,default,,0,0,0,,He kept his head down\Nto wait for the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔を伏して待った
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:50.12,default,,0,0,0,,...to get himself into a fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.00,default,,0,0,0,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね　クズ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.51,default,,0,0,0,,Die, garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この待ちこそが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジのファインプレー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.74,default,,0,0,0,,This waiting game was\Nfine play by Kaiji indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄に落ちろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:00.75,default,,0,0,0,,Meet your doom! Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:12.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカな… どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:12.16,default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… 待て
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:14.89,default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.40,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうひと勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　戻れ カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.63,default,,0,0,0,,One more time!\NYeah! Come back, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:30.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑さん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.97,default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バランス理論の内にひそむ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬかるみ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:33.63,default,,0,0,0,,The bog that lurks within\Nthe theory of balance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:38.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１度 深くはまった足は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:38.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たやすく抜けない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:37.25,default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to get out\Nonce you're in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:41.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜならバランスが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:41.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思考を支配する
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:41.62,default,,0,0,0,,With balance dominating\None's thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その世界観 理論 常識では
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.29,default,,0,0,0,,the idea that all the cards\Nare Scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.63,default,,0,0,0,,...totally defies his common sense,\Ntheory and perspective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてチョキなどということは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あり得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと 考えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.27,default,,0,0,0,,That's why he'll never\Nbelieve in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:54.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:54.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうチョキは出ない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.23,default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.73,default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any more Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:58.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セット
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:58.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４枚チョキだけは絶対にない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:54.73,default,,0,0,0,,Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.34,default,,0,0,0,,He can't possibly have 4 Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.47,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３連続で同じ手が来たから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.81,default,,0,0,0,,Having gone through\Nthe same thing thrice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:10.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう同じ手は来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.05,default,,0,0,0,,there's no way it would\Nhappen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:14.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルでは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:14.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この考え方は最も危険
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:13.82,default,,0,0,0,,This kind of thinking is the most\Ndangerous in gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキはない　チョキは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.05,default,,0,0,0,,There's no Scissors!\NNo Scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はまり込み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抜けられない崩壊への道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:26.37,default,,0,0,0,,There's no escape from the path to\Ndestruction once you're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルという魔性が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せせら笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.47,default,,0,0,0,,The devilish nature of gambling\Nmocked him in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:33.37,default,,0,0,0,,Why is that so?!\NWhy are all 4 cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして４枚も？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然さ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然… 偶然だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:35.97,default,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:38.57,default,,0,0,0,,Coincidence? Coincidence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:46.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり あんたの読み…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:46.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理論は間違ってなんかいない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:45.33,default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake in your\Nprediction theoretically!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも一歩狂えば そこが盲点だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.32,default,,0,0,0,,But if you miss a step,\Nyour blind spot appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間は理論ってやつを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１度 正しいと信じ込んじまうと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.77,default,,0,0,0,,Once one believes that\Na theory is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:55.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか疑わなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.62,default,,0,0,0,,it's difficult to doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ましてや その理論で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ってきたやつとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:21:00.16,default,,0,0,0,,It's even more so for someone\Nwho used that theory to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なおさら…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.88,default,,0,0,0,,His belief in the theory\Nmade him defenseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理論あるが故に無防備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 理論を逆手に取った２連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.90,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji used that to his advantage\Nto gain 2 straight wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 彼らを待ち受ける運命は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:11.54,default,,0,0,0,,But the destiny waiting\Nfor them is still dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ暗く出口は見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.41,default,,0,0,0,,without a slit of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この無限に続く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,漆黒の闇のように…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:17.17,default,,0,0,0,,Like an infinite tunnel\Nof darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回｢破綻｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.60,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Failure.
